   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_3_00032"/>An Dr. Rich. Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_3_00033"/><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L00588-1"/><date>12/IX 96</date><note type="textConst" corresp="T_L00588-1">auf der Rückseite des Umschlags</note></dateline><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_3_00034"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00588-1"/><date when="1896-09-13">So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00588-1">Der <date>13. 9. 1896</date> war ein
                     Sonntag, <rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs> irrt sich mit der
                     Beschriftung »<quote><date>12/IX 96</date></quote>«.</note>. – <time>½ 6. <hi rend="latintype">N. M.</hi></time></dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute> wie ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> man nicht
               einmal eine Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t zu Haus la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en wo man zu finden wäre! Ich ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>e per Rad von <rs ref="#pmb968" type="place">Mödling</rs> – <pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_3_00035"/><rs ref="#pmb24686" type="person">Tini</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb44715" type="place">Alland</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb47414" type="place">Neuhaus</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40112" type="place">Potten<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40115" type="place">Antonsga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 4</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb680" type="place">Franzensga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 54</rs> –</p><p>Der Doctor <rs ref="#pmb12740" type="person">Schwarzkopf</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t auch da, der grüßt
               Sie, aber nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o herzlich wie ich.</p><closer>Ihr <signed>ArthSch</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
